The 3D Cubic game contains following files:

3DCUBIC.EXE    -- Cubic Game
3DCUBIC.HLP    -- Online help file for Cubic Game
README.BAT     -- Introduction to Cubic Game and Instructions to play
                  Just type README, and it will show you all the help
                  you will need to play this game.
INSTALL.BAT    -- Batch file that installs Cubic Game on hard disk
INSTALL2.BAT   -- Supplementary batch file needed for INSTALL.BAT
GO.BAT         -- Batch file that invokes Cubic Game
                  To execute Cubic Game, just type GO and press ENTER.
3DCUBIC.ICN    -- Cubic Game icon for Microsoft Windows
REGISTER.FRM   -- Registeration form to license this game.
SOLVED.GAM     -- One saved Cubic Game to show the example of
                  solved game.
PACKAGE.LST    -- The file you are reading now.

